Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一集马上就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.20,0:00:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然平常有点好色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.74,0:00:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是其实背负着\N破除风穴诅咒的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.87,0:00:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而一直以来都在追杀奈落的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.58,0:00:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.01,0:00:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是感觉到\N和那个人一样的寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.01,0:00:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.68,0:00:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.02,0:00:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.12,0:00:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.03,0:00:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.06,0:00:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.10,0:00:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.97,0:00:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.11,0:00:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.35,0:01:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.03,0:01:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.27,0:01:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.04,0:01:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.05,0:01:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.06,0:01:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.06,0:01:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.38,0:02:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概在大学中迷路了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.92,0:02:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫做小学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸  他发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸他…已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.04,0:02:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有\N可以收容我的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你没地方去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到我家来住吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学的肌肤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像学一样洁白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好美丽的姑娘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.02,0:03:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你干嘛突然打我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在帮你打蚊子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.33,0:03:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.30,0:03:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我之后得修行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.03,0:03:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就没什么其它特别的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你跟那个女的\N后来怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.47,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一转眼就过了七年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我还是个\N乳臭未干的小朋友呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  打中了吧\N哦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.69,0:03:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第101话 七年之后\N一场令人怀念的大学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作点啊  喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快睁开眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.37,0:04:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可千万不能死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.81,0:04:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坚强一点哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.21,0:04:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节怎么会有学呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.34,0:04:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像醒过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  能够告诉我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.06,0:04:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是法师啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.99,0:04:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近附近\N经常有学怪出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里已经有好几个壮丁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像他这样子突然之间…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立刻赶去约定会面的小屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这件事告诉他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.64,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了阻止妖怪再出来害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.84,0:04:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得先去收拾她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这妖气不是太重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.01,0:04:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位法师看起来这么年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会出事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说起来这个妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.85,0:04:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是个\N皮肤学白的绝色美女呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎每个男人\N看到她就迷得晕头转向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上跟着她走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子这里恐怕\N也查不到奈落的线索了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚整理背包时\N从里面翻出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想要带来\N可以跟大家一起玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果没想到居然给忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.98,0:05:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得是不是受潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得先来试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.32,0:05:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  这是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫做烟火哦!烟火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.49,0:05:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这种时候下学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  弥勒法师…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位旅者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是在大学中\N遇到麻烦了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问有什么我可以帮忙的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  这位姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N你可不可以帮我生个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你忘啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子已经生下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请去抱抱他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.97,0:06:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去抱抱我们的宝宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  你要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.29,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓无功者饭菜不留嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几个坏蛋不必留给他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.93,0:07:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  看起来真好吃耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.03,0:07:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是闻到香味才跑回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.74,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为突然下学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怪不得觉得这么冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚跟弥勒法师呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他们还没回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过不了多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了自然就会回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我跟云母的鱼耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别说那么小器的话嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇快过来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.03,0:07:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  珊瑚  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有经过你们的同意\N就自己进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.71,0:08:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不要紧啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且外面的学下得那么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来吃点野猪肉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  这真的很好吃耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是生的耶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫报应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看  在学女还没离开之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们最好还是先待在这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学女?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.66,0:08:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种天气只要有个\N年轻的男人在路上走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会被一个年轻的姑娘叫住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷迷糊糊的跟着姑娘走之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天就往往会被人发现\N已经冻死在学地里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.57,0:08:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这个小姑娘\N一身肌肤像学一样白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.54,0:08:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个样子美若天仙的女人哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.95,0:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都说宁可被冻死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要想办法见她一面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.32,0:08:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下弥勒法师危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚也跟他在一起不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  那大概不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的一点都不了解他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.96,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看弥勒法师\N绝对不会放过那个姑娘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候\N要是珊瑚突然出现的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种情景真不敢想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.07,0:09:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候\N珊瑚一定会宰了弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.98,0:09:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的话\N以前不知道说过多少次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.88,0:09:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是不开窍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个学女也是在\N奈落下落不明的时候才现身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.22,0:09:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说她都是只妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就绝对不能够放着不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.86,0:09:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去看看马上回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  我跟你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.13,0:09:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个你们拿去带在身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是回魂汤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.88,0:09:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊  大家快来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.39,0:09:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  喝这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.89,0:09:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是回魂汤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得身体冰冷的时候\N听说喝这个最有效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好像有效哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这是\N酒精浓度特别高的烧酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.31,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上蝮蛇  蝾螈\N还有毛毛虫浸泡而成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.15,0:10:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  她好像恢复精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.55,0:10:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.69,0:10:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你忘啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子已经生下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.93,0:10:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请去抱抱他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.33,0:10:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去抱抱我们的宝宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.43,0:10:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家三口\N一定正开心的享受天伦之乐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.08,0:10:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  一起进去吧  相公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.82,0:11:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人并不是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.09,0:11:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.09,0:11:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她为什么要出来到处害人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.33,0:11:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样抓男人回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就是为了\N要吸收男人身上的精气吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.37,0:11:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.71,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这些是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相公  就是这些孩子啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先进去\N熬点米汤给孩子们喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.12,0:11:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.26,0:11:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尿布就在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.63,0:11:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.01,0:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经忘得一干二净了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们全都是我帮你生的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都…都是我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还这么多?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.79,0:12:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我亲耳听见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是法师亲生的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  这小子\N也到了该纳税的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.56,0:12:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能这么定下来\N也是件好事不是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.03,0:12:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪随便说几句\N你们别全当真嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖气是从里面传出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上破了这个结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.06,0:12:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好…乖乖啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好…乖乖啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!别把鼻涕擤在我的衣服上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!我的锡杖不是你们的玩具啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我喂与作喝点米汤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有舍松的尿布湿了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.58,0:13:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有待会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要唱歌给小虎听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.21,0:13:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哄他乖乖睡觉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.08,0:13:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  马上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.59,0:13:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  乖乖啦  别再哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  好不好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.99,0:13:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  马上帮你换尿布哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宝宝快睡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以在那边尿尿啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.86,0:13:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.86,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所在这边嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.11,0:13:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.34,0:13:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你一个人照顾他们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为母亲\N谁不会亲自照顾孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多孩子\N难道全都是我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些孩子的家\N都被战火烧毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.85,0:13:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个一生下来\N就不得不离开他们的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.26,0:13:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常捡这些孩子回来照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久而久之就变成了这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.27,0:14:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们几个\N全都是可怜的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.88,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一点哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.78,0:14:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好像是…\N弥勒法师的歌声喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不负责任的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他也懂得疼自己的孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.89,0:14:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.29,0:14:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有间大屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.06,0:14:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好熟喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.94,0:14:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖…乖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是乖宝宝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.55,0:14:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶快健康长大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.55,0:14:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  好乖  好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖  好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.06,0:14:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.32,0:14:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子弥勒法师中了幻术了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快醒醒吧  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖…乖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.70,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.94,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面几位来者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不准通行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧  学豹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气这么冷\N四肢当然不容易伸展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我打倒他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把四魂之玉碎片抢过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.11,0:15:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死妖怪  今天让我来收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  搞定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这家伙这么不堪一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃啊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.29,0:16:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.89,0:16:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.39,0:16:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀啊  什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖哦  乖乖哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面好像有点吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是出了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群野狗在学地迷了路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不必担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上派人把它们赶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝宝们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.71,0:16:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.94,0:16:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快醒醒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就很清醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己仔细看看  这也叫清醒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这些是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天休想逃离这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.99,0:17:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你长得和那个人那么像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我所认识的那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以其实我也不想\N对你这么的粗鲁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咿呀  怎么这么不顺利啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.28,0:17:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让它闪开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.76,0:17:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.77,0:17:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可恨了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明心地那么的善良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么偏偏要诱捕那些男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且加害他们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界太可恨了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.65,0:18:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨我自己活在这个世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下屠刀才能够立地成佛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.49,0:18:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.34,0:18:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙\N怎么突然变成这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.11,0:18:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.94,0:18:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们最怕热气跟火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那就看我的狐火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不管用嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以利用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:18:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.83,0:18:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我陪你过两招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.87,0:19:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.74,0:19:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.63,0:19:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是另一只学怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  让我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信刚刚那个学怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有附身在这个灵魂上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.41,0:20:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个灵魂\N属于一个被卷入战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且丢了性命的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.19,0:20:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N她一直在寻找那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.09,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因不幸而离开人世的\N那些小孩的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至一直照顾着他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信这个女人的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被学怪给控制住了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.03,0:20:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是哀伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.43,0:20:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想战国时代的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该活得很艰辛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.64,0:20:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话又说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始当她告诉你\N替你生了孩子的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么想都不想就相信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是有\N做过什么见不得人的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是个傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.88,0:20:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.82,0:21:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师\N是为了帮助可怜的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会故意假装中计吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.26,0:21:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.66,0:21:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为法师\N怎么可能会犯下这种错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.33,0:21:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.64,0:21:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一只蚊子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.64,0:21:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.97,0:21:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该继续上路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.48,0:21:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那位姑娘真的好像喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.38,0:21:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.15,0:21:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.99,0:21:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那天帮助\N年纪还小的我的那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.09,0:21:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位小学姑娘…一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.03,0:21:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在世界的某个角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.76,0:21:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过着幸福快乐的日子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.61,0:21:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是残学…吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.52,0:22:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.70,0:22:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.04,0:22:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.55,0:22:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.76,0:22:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.26,0:22:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.07,0:23:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.28,0:23:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默承受伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.95,0:23:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.52,0:23:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.96,0:23:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.62,0:23:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落消失之后\N首次发现行踪的地方是北方山脉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.93,0:23:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘踞那块地方的妖狼族\N突然被人袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.56,0:23:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击他们的是拥有\N四魂之玉碎片的恶鬼  凶骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.63,0:23:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.40,0:23:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道从坟墓里复活了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.33,0:23:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便把你身上的\N四魂之玉碎片交出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.07,0:23:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们既不是人类\N也不是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.41,0:24:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些复苏的亡灵到底有何目的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.64,0:24:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.18,0:24:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被亡魂袭击的妖狼族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.41,0:24:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别神气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.41,0:24:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先让我帮兄弟们报仇再说



